Countach. #

No idea if this is official yet, but… 

What do you think guys, if it is, did they pull it off? 
The one thing really sticking out like a sore thumb in my opinion are those Sian style taillights. I was hoping to see something a bit more… vertically oriented this time around. What do I know? Fingers crossed. 🤞🏼😂
